IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. TC201C.
DATA DIVISION.
WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
*> RESOLVED COPYBOOK CUSTREC:
*> 03 CUSTOMER-NAME PIC X(20).
*> 03 CUSTOMER-BAL  PIC 9(7)V99.
*> CUSTOMER-BAL displays as seven integer digits, a decimal point, and two fractional digits.
*> The fixture balance bytes 000123456 must display exactly as 0001234.56.
01 CUSTOMER-IN.
   COPY CUSTREC.
PROCEDURE DIVISION.
    ACCEPT CUSTOMER-IN.
    DISPLAY "NAME=" CUSTOMER-NAME.
    DISPLAY "BAL=" CUSTOMER-BAL.
    STOP RUN.
